### Replace {token} and optionally {baseUrl}. Default baseUrl = http://localhost:3004/api

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3004/api
@token = your-auth-token-here
@from = 2025-01-01
@to = 2025-01-31

### Inventory: valuation over time
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/stats/valuation-over-time?date_from={{from}}&date_to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inventory: top items by value
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/stats/top-by-value?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inventory: stock movement
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/stats/stock-movement?date_from={{from}}&date_to={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Accounting: revenue & expenses over time
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounting/reports/revenue-expenses-over-time?from_date={{from}}&to_date={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Accounting: expense by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounting/reports/expense-by-category?from_date={{from}}&to_date={{to}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inventory stats (includes total_stock_value, total_stock_quantity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
